quran[9{c,v,t}:
61,6,"aur yaad karo eesa Ibn maryam ki woh baat jo is ne kahi thi ke"" ae bani Israel , mein tumhari taraf Allah ka bheja howa rasool hon, tasdeeq karne wala hon uss Touraat ki jo mujh se pehlay aayi hui mojood hai, aur basharat dainay wala hon aik rasool ki jo mere baad aeye ga jis ka naam Ahmed hoga magar jab woh un ke paas khuli khuli nishanain le kar aaya to unhon ne kaha yeh to Sarih dhoka hai"
61,7,ab bhala uss shakhs se bara zalim aur kon hoga jo Allah par jhutay bohtan bandhay halaank usay islam ( Allah ke agay sir itaat jhuka dainay ) ki dawat di ja rahi ho? aisay zaalmon ko Allah hadaayat nahi diya karta
61,8,"yeh log apne mun ki phoonko se Allah ke noor ko bujhana chahtay hain, aur Allah ka faisla yeh hai ke woh apne noor ko pawwa phela kar rahay ga khuwa kafiroon ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho"
61,9,wohi to hai jis ne apne rasool ko hadaayat aur deen haq ke sath bheja hai taakay usay poooray ke poooray deen par ghalib kar day khuwa mushriqeen ko yeh kitna hi nagawaar ho
61,10,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, mein batau tum ko woh tijarat jo tumhe azaab alim se bacha day ?"
61,11,"imaan lao Allah aur is ke rasool par, aur jehaad karo Allah ki raah mein apne malon se aur apni jaanun se yahi tumahray liye behtar hai agar tum jano"
61,12,"Allah tumahray gunah maaf kar day ga, aur tum ko aisay baghoon mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi, aur abdi qiyam kijannaton mein behtareen ghar tumhe ataa farmaiye ga yeh hai barri kamyabi"
61,13,"aur woh doosri cheez jo tum chahtay ho woh bhi tumhe day ga, Allah ki taraf se nusrat aur qareeb hi mein haasil ho jaane wali fatah ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, ahal imaan ko iss ki basharat day do"
61,14,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah ke madadgaar bano, jis terhan eesa Ibn maryam ne hawarion ko khitaab kar ke kaha tha :"" kon hai Allah ki taraf ( bulanay ) mein mera madadgaar ?"" aur hawarion ne jawab diya tha :"" hum hain Allah ke madadgaar"" uss waqt bani Israel ka aik giroh imaan laya aur dosray giroh ne inkaar kya phir hum ne imaan laane walon ki unn ke dushmanon ke muqablay mein taied ki aur wohi ghalib ho kar rahay"
